OL,3,CMacron sets out plan for more French
OL,4,Cbabies amid falling birth rate
OL,6,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron wants
OL,7,Fto offer free fertility checks to
OL,8,Fpeople aged 18 to 25 to boost the
OL,9,Fcountry's declining birth rate
OL,11,FBy ITV News Digital Video Producer
OL,12,FIsaine Blatry
OL,14,FPresident Emmanuel Macron has unveiled
OL,15,Fa comprehensive plan to combat
OL,16,FFrance's dwindling birth rate.
OL,18,FThe country's birth rate has hit its
OL,19,Flowest point since World War II,
OL,20,Fdeclining by 7% last year.
