OL,3,CMacron sets out plan for more French
OL,4,Cbabies amid falling birth rate
OL,6,FNow the president's initiative aims to
OL,7,Freverse that trend by encouraging
OL,8,Fcouples to have children sooner.
OL,10,FCentral to Macron's strategy is the
OL,11,Fintroduction of free fertility checks
OL,12,Ffor individuals aged between 18 and 25.
OL,14,FThe plan is to empower young adults
OL,15,Fwith information about their
OL,16,Freproductive health, potentially
OL,17,Fenabling them to make informed
OL,18,Fdecisions about family planning at an
OL,19,Fearlier stage in their lives.
