OL,3,CMacron sets out plan for more French
OL,4,Cbabies amid falling birth rate
OL,6,FThe decline in birth rates in France
OL,7,Fis attributed to various factors,
OL,8,Fincluding shifting societal norms and
OL,9,Fincreasing financial pressures.
OL,11,FMacron's plan seeks to alleviate the
OL,12,Ffinancial burdens associated with
OL,13,Fraising a family by offering financial
OL,14,Fsupport for new parents.
OL,16,FSurrogacy, however, is excluded from
OL,17,Fthe plan due to ethical concerns.
