OL,3,CMacron sets out plan for more French
OL,4,Cbabies amid falling birth rate
OL,6,FMacron claimed surrogacy is "not
OL,7,Fcompatible with the dignity of women"
OL,8,Fand equated it to "turning their
OL,9,Fbodies into commodities".
OL,11,FThe plans also emphasises the
OL,12,Fimportance of paternal involvement in
OL,13,Fa child's life.
OL,15,FMacron is proposing the introduction
OL,16,Fof a "duty to visit" for fathers,
OL,17,Fwhich would require them to actively
OL,18,Fparticipate in their children's lives.
