OL,3,CMacron sets out plan for more French
OL,4,Cbabies amid falling birth rate
OL,6,FWhile Macron's initiative represents a
OL,7,Fproactive response to France's
OL,8,Fdemographic challenges, its
OL,9,Feffectiveness remains uncertain.
OL,11,FSimilar trends of declining birth
OL,12,Frates have been observed in other
OL,13,FEuropean countries, including the UK,
OL,14,Fwhere efforts to reverse the trend
OL,15,Fhave yet to materialise on a
OL,16,Fsignificant scale.
